data.description: WELCOME TO BIJOU CREEK. THIS BRAND NEW DEVELOPMENT IS LOCATED 40 MINUTES EAST OF DENVER. DEVELOPMENT CONSISTS OF NEW TOWN-HOMES (4 PER BUILDING). 56 UNITS IN ALL. PAVED ROADS W/ SIDEWALKS. STANDARD 2 CAR ATTACHED GARAGES. ADJOINS BRAND NEW K-12 SCHOOL. PRICED FROM THE MID 200'S. ALL MODELS COME STANDARD WITH SLAB GRANITE COUNTER-TOPS, HARD WOOD CABINETS, TILE FLOORING, LAMINATE FLOORING, WALL TO WALL CARPETING AND LANDSCAPED FRONT YARD. YOU WILL BE AMAZED WITH THE SPACE THIS BIJOU CREEK TOWN-HOME MODEL PROVIDES. ENTERING THE HOUSE YOU ARE WELCOMED TO THE THE LARGE FAMILY ROOM WHICH IS OPEN TO THE DINING AREA AND UPGRADED KITCHEN. THE MAIN FLOOR ALSO FEATURES A 1/2 BATHROOM, LAUNDRY ROOM AND ACCESS TO THE COVERED FRONT PORCH AND OVERSIZED ATTACHED 2 CAR GARAGE. UPSTAIRS YOU WILL FIND THE MASTER BEDROOM, LARGE FULL BATH, 1 ADDITIONAL BEDROOM, LOFT (OPTIONAL NON-CONFORMING 3rd BEDROOM 6'X8' AREA WITH AN OVERSIZED CLOSET), STORAGE CLOSET, AND LAUNDRY ROOM.  DON'T MISS OUT!!
